---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about this blog and its author.">
  <div class="prose-xl prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-(--color-text) mb-8">
      About This Blog
    </h1>
    <p>
      This blog is dedicated to sharing my journey and experiences in web
      development.
    </p>
    <p>
      I cover topics such as frontend frameworks, backend development, and best
      practices.
    </p>
    <p>Feel free to explore the posts and leave your feedback!</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-(--color-text) mt-12 mb-6">
      About Me
    </h2>
    <p>
      I'm a passionate web developer with a love for learning and sharing
      knowledge.
    </p>
    <p>When I'm not coding, I enjoy hiking and photography.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
